 <section class="medicine-app common_section" style="background:#fff;" id="md-solution1">
            <div class="container" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork">
                <header class="text-center">
					<div>
						<span itemprop="keywords"><h2 style="font-family: brandon-grotesque, sans-serif;font-style: normal;font-weight: 700;">TELEMEDICINE <span itemprop="">APPLICATION SOFTWARE DEVELOPMENT SOLUTIONS IN <span itemprop="contentLocation">NEW YORK</span></h2></span>
					</div>
                    <p lang="en-us">If you want an avant-garde healthcare system with a modern UI and robust architecture then SISGAIN’s <strong><a href="https://sisgain.com/telemedicine" style="color:black;">telemedicine</a></strong> applications should be your first pick. Our HIPAA compliant software for telehealth is building in a way to provide high-quality virtual care to our patients and you can also optimize your clinic’s operations. SISGAIN is a <span itemprop="keywords">top telehealth app development in New York</span> that extends a feature-packed yet inexpensive telemedicine solution that provides a bug-free and hassle-free user experience across every platform like Android, iOS, or the website.
                    </p>
