                            <li class="wow animated slideInRight" data-wow-duration="1.8s" data-wow-delay="0s" style="visibility: hidden; animation-duration: 1.8s; animation-delay: 0s; animation-name: none; margin-top:-30px;    color: #000;"><b>2.</b>SISGAIN’s<span itemprop="keywords"><strong> telemedicine app developers in New York</strong></span> will help the customers to improve their business and stay ahead in this competitive market. </li>
                            <li class="wow animated slideInRight" data-wow-duration="2.0s" data-wow-delay="0s" style="visibility: hidden; animation-duration: 2s; animation-delay: 0s; animation-name: none;  margin-top:-30px;    color: #000;"><b>3.</b> If you want to expand your reach to people then our hardworking and robust team will guide you towards it.  </li>
                            <li class="wow animated slideInRight" data-wow-duration="2.2s" data-wow-delay="0s" style="visibility: hidden; animation-duration: 2.2s; animation-delay: 0s; animation-name: none;margin-top:-30px;    color: #000;"><b>4.</b>Even if you are an individual physician or a hospital, or a small clinic SISGAIN’s<strong> <span itemprop="keywords">HIPAA compliant telehealth software systems</span></strong> have multiple features for the clients. </li>
                            <li class="wow animated slideInRight" data-wow-duration="2.4s" data-wow-delay="0s" style="visibility: hidden; animation-duration: 2.4s; animation-delay: 0s; animation-name: none;margin-top:-30px;    color: #000;"><b>5.</b>You can easily book an appointment, get convenient access to the appointment history, receive notifications, get to know about the upcoming appointments, have access to doctor’s profile, you can securely upload health reports and many more.</li>
